><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"118b503e435040f3a00ff61c154b1e6ca6c57e39","tid":2221963,"uid":254165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T18:49:30.000Z","msg":"花地瑪幾時先兌現 忍撚夠呢條仆街教宗"},{"pid":"e6d0e290bc2fff802c5df1a5a069efc3b97a2e85","tid":2221963,"uid":167928,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T18:49:51.000Z","msg":"「這也不足為怪，因為連撒旦也裝作光明的天使。」<br />\n哥林多後書 11:14 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cnbible.com/2_corinthians/11-14.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcnbible.com%2F2_corinthians%2F11-14.htm&d=Wx0cKZaQlto0GELw8F4hIeQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=c5baa8eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cnbible.com/2_corinthians/11-14.htm</a>"},{"pid":"74093db3aea879900a5509ab78289940a16792e9","tid":2221963,"uid":167928,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T18:54:41.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">當保羅寫哥林多後書的時候，有一班人稱自己為使徒，也傳耶穌，也傳福音，表面看來和使徒保羅一樣</span>。但是保羅指出這些人所傳講的，不是純正的道，不是真理。這些人乃是<span class=\"red\">假使徒，他們行事詭詐</span>，實際上他們是<span class=\"red\">撒但的差役</span>。所以保羅警告哥林多教會，要會分辨這些假冒，要提防仇敵的各樣計謀，<span class=\"red\">不要因他外表好看、話語動聽，就相信他們的話</span>。心思要在真理這一邊，單單順服基督，如此撒但就失敗，我們就得勝。<br />\n<br />\n　<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.churchinhk.org/book-resource/裝作光明的天使/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.churchinhk.org%2Fbook-resource%2F%E8%A3%9D%E4%BD%9C%E5%85%89%E6%98%8E%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A9%E4%BD%BF%2F&d=Wx0cKZaQlto0GELw8F4hIeQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=2fe362d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.churchinhk.org/book-resource/裝作光明的天使/</a>"},{"pid":"4d2fd5a6a9f263a9649512f28b8bffcd46965eb6","tid":2221963,"uid":239270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T18:56:05.000Z","msg":"係上帝安排我奶共，點解要見你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b475450e0fcc0ae099701bd6cc326b7a76a87e50","tid":2221963,"uid":140924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime